name: NY City Dating
short_description:
NY City Dating an open source dating website, based on osDate and Fusion.

This is still under development, please register for the support site to help with contributions to this project.

UPDATE April 14 2012.

Due to the lack of interest in this on the development side of life, is has been decided to remove this until further notice. I am still working on this, but with other work commitments this will take time. If you are interested in assisting the development please contact me.
summary: Development ongoing, have removed unstable script until further notice
